---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AZVAI AI Playground | Vibecoding Portfolio"
  description="Purpose-driven AI experiments for leadership, learning systems, and practical change."
  current="home"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <img src="/assets/azvai_logo.png" alt="AZVAI logo" class="hero-logo" />
    <p class="eyebrow">ai.azvai.com</p>
    <h1>Purpose-driven vibecoding for learning systems change.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Practical AI experiments designed to help teams learn faster, decide better, and build resilient organizations.
      This is where strategy, systems thinking, and rapid prototyping meet.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="hero-banner">
    <img src="/assets/azvai_circulos.png" alt="AZVAI circles" />
    <div class="hero-banner-text">
      <h2>Built with intent. Tested through action.</h2>
      <p>
        From leadership tools to knowledge workflows, each build is an experiment in better decisions, stronger teams,
        and tech that serves people and planet.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>Explore</h2>
    <div class="line"></div>
  </div>

  <section class="grid" aria-label="Portfolio sections">
    <article class="card span-6">
      <div class="card-icon">&#9881;</div>
      <h3>Projects</h3>
      <p>Working experiments with architecture notes, implementation logic, and real-world learning loops.</p>
      <p class="kicker"><a href="/projects">Browse projects &rarr;</a></p>
    </article>

    <article class="card span-6">
      <div class="card-icon">&#9889;</div>
      <h3>Training Tools</h3>
      <p>Interactive AI-powered tools for leadership development, capability building, and organizational learning.</p>
      <p class="kicker"><a href="/training">Open training &rarr;</a></p>
    </article>

    <article class="card featured span-4">
      <h3>Guiding Ethos</h3>
      <p>Build useful technology that improves systems, empowers people, and creates measurable positive outcomes.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card span-4">
      <h3>Operating Stack</h3>
      <p>Astro frontend, GitHub versioning, Netlify deployment, and API-first workflows for rapid iteration.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card span-4">
      <h3>Direction of Travel</h3>
      <p>Evolve from demos into production-grade learning infrastructure that helps companies become learning organizations.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
